    public class ContainerDialog
extends org.eclipse.ui.dialogs.SelectionStatusDialog
    Select container rules, either from a list of globally defined rules or from local rules which may be created "on the fly" by this dialog. TODO: extend rule application to instances (problematic, since rules transformation is done on type level)
